REM Title: System summary
REM Author: Cypher
REM Description: Prints OS version, hostname, uptime, and CPU model. Quick
REM "what am I sitting at" snapshot for unfamiliar Macs.
REM Target: macOS
DELAY 500
GUI SPACE
DELAY 500
STRING Terminal
DELAY 1000
ENTER
DELAY 800
STRING clear; sw_vers; echo; scutil --get ComputerName; uptime; sysctl -n machdep.cpu.brand_string
ENTER
